items.title: Boba Fett Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Boba Fett wiki, the wiki for all things Boba Fett!
items.desc: The Boba Fett wiki is about the famous Star Wars character, Boba Fett. This wiki is devoted to offering information about Boba Fett and his exploits. Anyone can add, but please only add relevant information to this wiki. Any activity that offends other users or members of this wiki is banned. This wiki may contain inappropriate language.
